हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/hndnSg
show.description: Crown Ka Khel is the tale of the wealthy Singh family, where greed and betrayal tear relationships apart. A pregnant Soumya Devi, the true queen of the house, returns after years, only to be humiliated by Vani, Vikram Singh’s ambitious fiancée. When the truth explodes, a fiery battle begins for love, power, and the family’s throne. Watch now – a drama unlike anything you have ever seen.
